    ModelMesh["ModelMesh / KServe"] -->|gRPC<br/>8033/TCP| TGISAdapter
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|HTTP scrape<br/>8000/TCP /metrics| PromMetrics

    %% External dependencies
    Worker0 -->|NCCL| Worker1
    ModelExecutor -->|HTTPS/443| S3["S3 / Model Storage"]
    APIServer -.->|gRPC/4317| OTEL["OTEL Collector"]

